The paper proposes a new algorithm for online combinatorial optimization under semi-bandit feedback, which is a problem commonly studied in the machine learning community. The paper also discusses the use of importance weighting, which is a common technique in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves information theory (cs.IT) and computational complexity (cs.CC) in its analysis, which are also possible sub-categories.
